      "role": "user",
      "content": "i honestly dont know how much longer i can keep doing this. everything i worked for in the lab... the funding just dried up and the department is basically treating me like a ghost now. i feel like my whole life has been built on a foundation of sand and now it's just... gone. i'm so tired. not just sleepy, but like, soul-tired. i just want everything to stop. i just want the noise and the pressure to finally be quiet.",
