      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's just it... the \"path forward\" always feels like more work. more fighting, more explaining myself, more trying to rebuild something that's already broken. every time someone says things will get better, it just feels like they're asking me to sign up for more struggle. it's like... if you're drowning, people keep telling you to swim harder, but sometimes you just want to let the water take you so you don't have to fight the waves anymore. it seems so much more peaceful than this constant friction.",
